          "purpose": "describing",
          "value": "The `Diffeomorph` structure is parametrized by a smoothness level `n : ℕ∞ω`, so `M ≃ₘ^n⟮I, I'⟯ M'` is exactly a C^n-diffeomorphism.",
          "format": "text/plain"
        }
      ],
